msgid ""
"KAlgebra backend for Cantor. Lets you use the same language you use in the "
"KAlgebra application in Cantor worksheets."
msgstr ""
"KAlgebra bizkarraldekoa Cantor-rerako. KAlgebra aplikazioan erabiltzen duzun "
"lengoaia bera Cantor-ren lan-orrietan erabiltzen uzten dizu."

